OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAbolish energy price cap,  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsays Scottish Power boss   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of one of the UK's biggest    
OL,6, energy companies has called for the    
OL,7, energy price cap to be abolished.      
OL,9,FKeith Anderson, chief executive of     
OL,10,FScottish Power, said the recent energy 
OL,11,Fcrisis had exposed deep flaws in the   
OL,12,Fway the energy market was structured.  
OL,14,FHe added there had been serious        
OL,15,Ffailures on the part of Ofgem.         
OL,17,FThe regulator said the price cap had   
OL,18,Fhelped to keep down costs for millions 
OL,19,Fof households.                         
